TO CREATE:

1. First create the storage class: kubectl create -f storageclass-fast-aws.yaml
2. Next create the claim: kubectl create -f mongodb-pvc-aws.yaml
3. Next create replicaset: kubectl create -f mongodb-rs-pv.yaml


TO DELETE: ( use word "delete" instead of "create" in above commands )
1. first delete replicaset
2. then delete claim
3. then delete storage class
